  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support the resilient livelihoods and safety of men and women most affected by conflict_CNEB</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project intends to bring in greater resilience for beneficiaries while dealing with effects of the conflict and violence arising out of the recent crisis. peace messages as well as reconciliation messages will contribute to peaceful coexistence at community level.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will organize sensitization activities on peace building using peace messages for different structures in the province. Training for representatives of structures on peace building will be organized as well as meetings at provincial level in order to sharing best testimonies on peace building. Local media will also be engaged on peace and reconciliation.</narrative>
  </description>
